  "@type": "Service",
  "name": "Roof Repair in South Jordan, UT",
  "description": "Emergency roof repair, storm damage restoration, and roof inspections serving South Jordan, Utah including the Daybreak community. Same-day response. Free estimates.",
  "areaServed": {
