---

<BaseLayout
  title="Roof Repair in South Jordan, UT | Sandy Roofing Pros — Emergency & Storm Damage"
  description="Emergency roof repair and storm damage restoration in South Jordan, Utah. Licensed local contractors serving Daybreak and all South Jordan neighborhoods. Free estimates."
  canonicalUrl="/areas/south-jordan"
>

  <!-- Local Service + Breadcrumb structured data -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(localServiceSchema)} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(breadcrumbSchema)} />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="area-hero" style="background-image: url('/images/hero-bg.jpg');">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="area-badge">📍 Serving South Jordan, UT — 84009</span>
      <h1>Roof Repair in South Jordan, UT — Emergency Service &amp; Storm Damage</h1>
      <p>
        South Jordan has grown fast — and new construction brings its own roofing risks.
        Flashing failures are common in the first few years. Daybreak sees frequent hail
        exposure from summer storms tracking northeast across the valley. Whether your
        home is brand-new or a decade old, storm damage is storm damage.
      </p>
      <div class="hero__ctas">
        <a href={phoneHref} class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">📞 Call Now for a Free Estimate</a>
        <a href="#get-estimate" class="btn btn--outline btn--lg">Get Instant Help Online</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust Bar -->
  <div class="trust-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <ul class="trust-bar__list">
        <li class="trust-bar__item"><span class="trust-bar__icon">⚡</span><span>Same-Day Response</span></li>
        <li class="trust-bar__item"><span class="trust-bar__icon">✅</span><span>Licensed Utah Contractors</span></li>
        <li class="trust-bar__item"><span class="trust-bar__icon">💲</span><span>Free Estimates</span></li>
        <li class="trust-bar__item"><span class="trust-bar__icon">🛡️</span><span>Insurance Claims Assisted</span></li>
        <li class="trust-bar__item"><span class="trust-bar__icon">📍</span><span>South Jordan, UT 84009</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About South Jordan Roofing -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <span class="section-heading__eyebrow">What's Unique About South Jordan</span>
        <h2>New Construction Doesn't Mean Storm-Proof</h2>
        <p>
          South Jordan is one of the fastest-growing cities in Salt Lake County.
          That growth creates specific roofing patterns worth understanding.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__body">
            <div class="service-card__icon">🏗️</div>
            <h3>New Build Flashing Failures</h3>
            <p>
              Flashing — the metal sealing around chimneys, vents, and skylights —
              is the most common installation failure in newer homes. It often holds
              for two or three years before a hard storm pulls it loose. By then,
              the builder's warranty is expired. This is one of the most common
              calls we get from South Jordan homeowners.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__body">
            <div class="service-card__icon">⛈️</div>
            <h3>Daybreak Hail Exposure</h3>
            <p>
              The Daybreak area and communities near the Mountain View Corridor
              sit in a flat, exposed section of the valley that gets full impact
              from summer storm cells. Hail that tracks northeast from Utah Lake
              hits South Jordan before it reaches Sandy or Draper.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__body">
            <div class="service-card__icon">🔍</div>
            <h3>Under-Inspected Roofs</h3>
            <p>
              Many South Jordan homeowners assume a newer roof doesn't need attention.
              That assumption costs money. A 5-year-old roof after a major hail season
              can have significant invisible damage — granule loss, bruised shingles —
              that shortens its life by years without a single leak appearing yet.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <span class="section-heading__eyebrow">What We Do in South Jordan</span>
        <h2>Roofing Services for South Jordan Homeowners</h2>
      </div>

      <ul class="why-list">
        <li class="why-item">
          <div class="why-item__icon">🚨</div>
          <div class="why-item__text">
            <h3>Emergency Leak Repair</h3>
            <p>Active leak anywhere in South Jordan — Daybreak, Oquirrh Commons, anywhere in 84009. Same-day dispatch available day and night.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="why-item">
          <div class="why-item__icon">🌩️</div>
          <div class="why-item__text">
            <h3>Storm &amp; Hail Damage</h3>
            <p>Post-storm inspection with full documentation. Our contractors know what South Jordan adjus­tors look for and document it correctly the first visit.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
